![Mexico](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c6fe47bc888a70c68e510c04a4997a8c4fd52aa9.png)

Addon for **Farmers Delight**.

Mexican's Delight is a mod that expands Farmers Delight by adding various Mexican food into the game. It adds new recipes and foods for every single piece of Mexican Food in the mod, leaving none unaccessible in survival mode. It adds the following unique foods, each with their own stats and properties;  
Tacos;  
Burritos;  
Chips;  
and Salsa.  

Dependencies:  
Farmers' Delight
